show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा।

show.description: A struggling college student falls for her intimidating yet irresistible professor, sparking a risky romance amid academic pressure and family drama. Their growing bond puts both their futures on the line.
